<<dialog "dinerChef">>Breakfast crowd doesn't quit.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Felt like nonstop out front too.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerChef">>Eggs. Always eggs. Everybody wants eggs a different way.<</dialog>>
