<<dialog "dinerChef">>Morning rush hit different today.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Yeah, we were slammed.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerChef">>Some guy sent back his toast. Twice.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>What was wrong with it?<</dialog>>
